{"title":"犁耙飘香","authors":["熊明修"],"dates":[{"year":1992,"month":1,"day":27}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁耙飘香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熊明修"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冰封雪冻的季节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挂在屋子里的犁耙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暗自飘香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水和泥土还很寒冷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们从袖管里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抽出温暖的手指"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抚摸犁耙的思想"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁耙教给我们最初的智慧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是热爱土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加入了犁耙养活的民族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就要跟随犁耙走向土地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以大将风度"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"统率雨水阳光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕耘播种的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光明或黑暗无法左右我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多情的种子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过一些灾害　以一还十"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起到达耐人咀嚼的地方"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一切逐渐丰满起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁耙突然停止了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蹒跚的步履"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以至离开犁耙的日子愈深"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的感觉愈清香"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}